	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ben je al klaar? <delay20 />Met het maken van <tag a="50" b="19" arg="0x12 0xcd00 0x6 0x64 0x69 0x65 0x6 0x64 0x61 0x74 0x6 0x64 0x69 0x65" /> <tag a="50" b="23" arg="0xcd03" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />, bedoel ik.</message>
